# Server Config
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# Database Config
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=123456
DB_NAME=coding_game
DB_PORT=3306

# JWT Secret
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_key_change_this_in_production
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# CORS
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
```

**Lưu ý:** Thay `DB_PASSWORD` bằng mật khẩu MySQL của bạn!

